{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji16","name":"毛泽东全集第16卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/maoquanji16.pdf"],"article":{"title":"给续范享“的信","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"给续范亭的信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1941年9月22日）范亭同志："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大示敬悉。已交组织部陈云同志考虑，俟得覆后再行奉告，你的要求是正当的。我的风湿近日采用洗澡，晒太阳，按摩，吃水果诸法，颇有起色，知注敬告。关向应同志已动身来延，不日可到。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敬问健好！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"九月二十二日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[1]续范亭（1893-1947)，名培模，山西省醇县（今原平县）人。1947年9月12日逝世。临终前，遗书请求加入中国共产党，经中共中央批"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1941,"month":9,"day":22}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":240,"page_end":240},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"书信"}]}]}